------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
오늘 강의
    오늘의 강의: 유튜브 클론코딩: From #3.5 to #3.10
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Code Challenge
    Let's create our own middlewares!
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Tasks
    We will create 4 middlewares.
        URL Logger: This middleware should log the URL that is being visited.
        Time Logger: This middleware should log the year, month and day of the request.
        Security Logger: This middleware should log secure if the protocol is https else log insecure.
        Protector Middleware: This middleware should stop the user if it's trying to go to /protected
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Hints
    Express Reference (https://expressjs.com/en/api.html#req)
    Date (https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Examples
    For example, an http request to the / URL should log:
        Path:  /
        Time: 2021.4.25
        Insecure ❌
    If you don't submit the 4 middlewares the assignment will be marked as failed
